    {
      "text": "\n\n**Key Findings:**\n- **1,396 guests** acquired through APP135 promo code with **89.3% 30-day return rate**\n- Non-promo app users showed 85.2% retention\u2014**4.1 points lower**\n- APP135 users returned slightly faster (2.5 days average vs 0.4 days for non-promo)\n- First visit check averages were $19.17 for promo users vs $21.82 for non-promo (expected given discount structure)\n- Second visit checks normalized to $19.62 vs $21.91, showing sustained engagement\n\n## Digital Channel Performance (Q4 2025)\n\n",
